'''Goat Milk''' is an [[:Category:Animal Products|animal product]] obtained from a [[Goat]] by using a [[Milk Pail]].

When a goat has a sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship and mood]] level, it can produce a [[Large Goat Milk]], which is more valuable.

